pr_title: Google Summer of Code’22: Port fortran-lang.org to Sphinx
pr_body:
This PR is to port the Existing site of fortran-lang.org to sphinx.
This GSoC’22 project is done by Henil Shalin Panchal under the Guidance of GSoC mentors Sebastian Ehlert @awvwgk and Rohit Goswami @HaoZeke .I request all the members of the organisation fortran-lang @fortran-lang/admins @fortran-lang please review this PR and add suggestions and comments on this PR. 

https://summerofcode.withgoogle.com/programs/2022/projects/L28fukIz

**Live preview** of this PR is available at gh-pages of my repo : https://henilp105.github.io/webpage/en/index.html .

Thanks and Regards,
Henil Shalin Panchal

pr_title: Google Summer of Code’22: Port fortran-lang.org to Sphinx
pr_body:
This PR is to port the Existing site of fortran-lang.org to sphinx.
This GSoC’22 project is done by Henil Shalin Panchal under the Guidance of GSoC mentors Sebastian Ehlert @awvwgk and Rohit Goswami @HaoZeke .I request all the members of the organisation fortran-lang https://github.com/orgs/fortran-lang/teams/admins https://github.com/fortran-lang please review this PR and add suggestions and comments on this PR.

https://summerofcode.withgoogle.com/programs/2022/projects/L28fukIz

This PR Fixes the Following Issues :
- [x] #6 
- [x] #7 
- [x] #9 
- [x] #10

Closes https://github.com/fortran-lang/webpage/pull/22   

as we have completely ported to myst-markdown This  also removes the need of API_token as we can use shield.io for packages. thus this reduces the number of get requests to 4 which is not even 1% of the limit so, we should not use API_TOKEN.

@awvwgk Sir, We would have to manually create a folder named pr in gh-pages as due to safe workflow only the output files are being commited and also we aren't even checking out the gh-pages branch thus as a one-time measure we would have to manually create pr folder.

@awvwgk Sir, thanks a lot for making the learn page in myst-markdown, It was an ideal exaple to help in other pages.

Thanks and Regards,
Henil Shalin Panchal

CC @awvwgk

pr_title: Google Summer of Code’22: Port fortran-lang.org to Sphinx
pr_body:
This PR is to port the Existing site of fortran-lang.org to sphinx.
This GSoC’22 project is done by Henil Shalin Panchal under the Guidance of GSoC mentors Sebastian Ehlert @awvwgk and Rohit Goswami @HaoZeke .I request all the members of the organisation fortran-lang https://github.com/orgs/fortran-lang/teams/admins https://github.com/fortran-lang please review this PR and add suggestions and comments on this PR.

https://summerofcode.withgoogle.com/programs/2022/projects/L28fukIz

This PR Fixes the Following Issues :
- [x] added pr preview banner for preview builds. (independent of the pydata theme version).
- [x] added documentation for pre-commit hooks.
- [x]  locked the dependency versions of packages.
- [x] Formated the html templates.
- [x] resolved the date error in newsletter of june 2022.
- [x] enabled build of all translations for build preview
- [x] resolved #29 (for index page)
- [x] added dependabot for requirements.txt 
- [x] updated translations

Thanks and Regards,
Henil Shalin Panchal

CC @awvwgk

pr_title: Google Summer of Code’22: Port fortran-lang.org to Sphinx
pr_body:
This PR is to port the Existing site of fortran-lang.org to sphinx.
This GSoC’22 project is done by Henil Shalin Panchal under the Guidance of GSoC mentors Sebastian Ehlert @awvwgk and Rohit Goswami @HaoZeke .I request all the members of the organisation fortran-lang https://github.com/orgs/fortran-lang/teams/admins https://github.com/fortran-lang please review this PR and add suggestions and comments on this PR.

https://summerofcode.withgoogle.com/programs/2022/projects/L28fukIz

This PR Fixes the Following Issues :
- [x] resolves the setup python bug #4 ( there was a bug in v4 which prevented the detection of python version , setting that version of python manually resolves the bug.)
- [x] resolves the ablog #36  dependabot pr. 
- [x] github pages url for pr preview.
- [x] resolves the learn section button translation bug
- [x] updated the translations for learn section button. 
- [x] shift from custom navbar to original navbar  
- [x] learn section dark theme color fixed.
- [x] resolves #39 

Thanks and Regards,
Henil Shalin Panchal

CC @awvwgk

pr_title: Google Summer of Code’22: Port fortran-lang.org to Sphinx
pr_body:
This PR is to port the Existing site of fortran-lang.org to sphinx.
This GSoC’22 project is done by Henil Shalin Panchal under the Guidance of GSoC mentors Sebastian Ehlert @awvwgk and Rohit Goswami @HaoZeke .I request all the members of the organisation fortran-lang https://github.com/orgs/fortran-lang/teams/admins https://github.com/fortran-lang please review this PR and add suggestions and comments on this PR.

https://summerofcode.withgoogle.com/programs/2022/projects/L28fukIz

This PR Fixes the Following Issues :
- [x] resolves #41
- [x] resolves #43 
- [x] set prettier in pre-commit hooks
- [x] prettified all the files.  
- [x] GNU license link in intrinsics.

Thanks and Regards,
Henil Shalin Panchal

CC @awvwgk

pr_title: Google Summer of Code’22: Port fortran-lang.org to Sphinx
pr_body:
This PR is to port the Existing site of fortran-lang.org to sphinx.
This GSoC’22 project is done by Henil Shalin Panchal under the Guidance of GSoC mentors Sebastian Ehlert @awvwgk and Rohit Goswami @HaoZeke .I request all the members of the organisation fortran-lang https://github.com/orgs/fortran-lang/teams/admins https://github.com/fortran-lang please review this PR and add suggestions and comments on this PR.

https://summerofcode.withgoogle.com/programs/2022/projects/L28fukIz

This PR Fixes the Following Issues :
- [x] resolves #56
- [x] resolves #115
- [x] resolves #116
- [x] resolves rss feed url on nav bar.
- [x] prettified files.
- [x] resolves #118

Thanks and Regards,
Henil Shalin Panchal

CC @awvwgk

pr_title: Google Summer of Code’22: Port fortran-lang.org to Sphinx
pr_body:
This PR is to port the Existing site of fortran-lang.org to sphinx.
This GSoC’22 project is done by Henil Shalin Panchal under the Guidance of GSoC mentors Sebastian Ehlert @awvwgk and Rohit Goswami @HaoZeke .I request all the members of the organisation fortran-lang https://github.com/orgs/fortran-lang/teams/admins https://github.com/fortran-lang please review this PR and add suggestions and comments on this PR.

https://summerofcode.withgoogle.com/programs/2022/projects/L28fukIz

This PR Fixes the Following Issues :
- [x] Fortran name in index page.
- [x] License Footer Bug fix.
- [x] webpage Contributor Graph repository.
- [x] resolve mail box colour 
- [x] resolves workflow delete preview bug
- [x] update translation po files
- [x] #131
- [x] #135   

Thanks and Regards,
Henil Shalin Panchal

CC @awvwgk  

Closes #131 
Closes #135

pr_title: Google Summer of Code’22: Port fortran-lang.org to Sphinx
pr_body:
This PR is to port the Existing site of fortran-lang.org to sphinx.
This GSoC’22 project is done by Henil Shalin Panchal under the Guidance of GSoC mentors Sebastian Ehlert @awvwgk and Rohit Goswami @HaoZeke .I request all the members of the organisation fortran-lang https://github.com/orgs/fortran-lang/teams/admins https://github.com/fortran-lang please review this PR and add suggestions and comments on this PR.

https://summerofcode.withgoogle.com/programs/2022/projects/L28fukIz

This PR Fixes the Following Issues :
- [x] resolves #120
- [x] resolves #122 
- [x]  resolves #130  
- [x] resole mail box colour 
- [x] documentation for learn section
- [x] resolves workflow delete preview bug
- [x] update translation po files

Thanks and Regards,
Henil Shalin Panchal

CC @awvwgk
